{"tid":696914,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盡情做愛OK！巴西為球員性生活開綠燈","createTime":"2018-06-10T13:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T02:00:02.000Z","uid":62257,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c813ff85249ae83a465e2c35de488d56b73e596","tid":696914,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2452544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2452544&d=0AsXtqbEEn5ui789sjoDzf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=273d0151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2452544&h=3c8a3acd\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2452544</a><br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕世界盃即將到來，各隊都正在積極備戰，不過對於球員的放鬆方式，每個國家都自有一套管理系統，來自南美洲的巴西就相當奔放，日前宣佈將不會禁止球員在盛會期間做愛，盼球員場上也能同樣拿出好表現。<br />\n<br />\n根據俄羅斯媒體指出，巴西國家隊日前針對球員的性生活進行解答，表示不會禁止球員在場下從事性愛，巴西隊醫甚至說，「性愛是很自然的一件事，我們隊上的年輕球員這麼多，又相當健康，用這機會做愛放鬆心情也是很正常的，沒有什麼問題。」<br />\n<br />\n不過巴西隊醫也強調，其實球員的性生活還是會受到管理，只是不會完全禁止性行為，如球員的另一半在比賽日將無法享受魚水之歡，只能在休息日時發洩精力。"},{"pid":"018f265dac24a8f8a4f468c8d87a33f057a68683","tid":696914,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46504b83594240163083f488f8b52a518115d24d","tid":696914,"uid":40624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"其實扑左野佢又點知？"},{"pid":"4c515a9cc539c54b6738880c26bd91052695d6a4","tid":696914,"uid":40839,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"46504b83594240163083f488f8b52a518115d24d","tid":696914,"uid":40624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"其實扑左野佢又點知？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:46:26.000Z","msg":"點知check唔到<br />\n你去睇中醫 佢把一把脈都知你琴晚有無扑野/打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b